routeFacts.name: Arosalinie
routeFacts.description: Arosalinie is a route Add-On for Train Sim World 2. Featured with the route is the RhB Ge 4/4 II. The track gauge for this line is 1,000 mm, instead of the standard 1,435 mm. This is the first route to use non-standard track gauge in Train Sim World 2.
routeInfo: The Arosalinie is a 26 kilometre metre gauge railway from the capital of Grab√ºnden Canton, Chur, to the ski resort of Arosa. The route is varied, with street running in Chur, along with mountainous sections, with tunnels and viaducts, including the famous Langwieser Viaduct.
